37c-1.163 1.72-3.585 5.3-3.585 7.524a5.544 5.544 0 0 0 3.423 5.114v2.804H11.021c-6.077 0-11.02 4.896-11.02 10.914 0 3.745 2 7.267 5.242 9.266v11.064c0 2.32 1.96 4.28 4.28 4.28H44.94c2.32 0 4.28-1.96 4.28-4.28v-10.97a10.905 10.905 0 0 0 5.35-9.37c-.114-6.013-5.107-10.904-11.129-10.904z" mask="url(#yotpo-birthday-icon-maskId)"></path></g></svg></div></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Birthday Bonus<br></strong>25 Points</p></div></div><div class="pagebuilder-column section--margin-top" data-content-type="column" data-appearance="full-height" data-background-images="{}" data-element="main" data-pb-style="PRW7009"><div data-content-type="html" data-appearance="default" data-element="main" data-decoded="true"><div class="yotpo-widget-campaign-widget-icon-container"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="58" height="58" viewbox="0 0 58 58" role="img" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="yotpo-widget-campaign-widget-icon" style="color: rgb(255, 184, 192);"><title>Facebook share icon</title><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M27.658 14.045v6.823l-.156.024c-7.308 1.125-11.295 2.635-15.894 6.609-4.53 3.915-7.145 8.775-8.537 14.982-.593 2.832 2.65 4.789 4.865 3.007 2.331-2 4.454-3.373 7.262-4.827l.88-.448 1.945-.962.29-.14c2.588-1.233 4.846-1.725 8.763-1.833l.632-.014v6.716c0 2.344 2.576 3.825 4.561 2.594l22.435-15.041c1.747-1.277 1.698-3.87-.05-5.042L32.33 11.524c-1.973-1.374-4.673.122-4.673 2.521zm4 1.843L51.257 29.03l-19.55 13.107.002-5.92a2.972 2.972 0 0 0-2.318-2.913l-.216-.048h-.22c-5.68 0-8.786.541-12.362 2.245l-1.797.882c-.55.273-.992.496-1.436.726l-.567.297c-1.864.99-3.48 1.977-5.058 3.133l.035-.111c1.304-4.003 3.344-7.214 6.454-9.902 4.114-3.555 7.588-4.781 14.864-5.827l.11-.019c1.425-.287 2.46-1.501 2.46-2.972v-5.821z"></path></svg></div></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Shop, Share &amp; Earn<br></strong>100 Points = $10</p></div></div></div></div><div class="text-block capsule-button capsule-button--pink centered-on-desktop--capsule-button centered-on-mobile--capsule-button section--margin-top" data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: center;"><a tabindex="0" href="/web/20230407022305/https://www.joahbeauty.com/loyalty">JOIN NOW</a></p></div></div></div><div data-content-type="row" data-appearance="contained" data-element="main"><div class="press-slider-row section--margin-top--double section--margin-bottom--double" data-enable-parallax="0" data-parallax-speed="0.5" data-background-images="{}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="Q3WWHOY"><div data-content-type="html" data-appearance="default" data-element="main" data-decoded="true"><!-- Press Carousel | CSS -->
<style>


.press-slider .owl-stage{
  display: flex;
  align-items: stretch; 
}
 
.press-slider-row h3{
  display: none;
}

.press-slider-container { 
  margin: 0 auto; 
}

.press-slider .item { 
  text-align: center; 
  display: flex; 
  flex-flow: column; 
  height: 100%;
}

.press-slider-thumbs{
  font-size: 24px;
  max-width: 49em;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

.press-slider-thumbs .item {    
  padding: 0px; 
  margin: 2px;  
  border-radius: 3px; 
  text-align: center; 
  cursor: pointer; 
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-content: center;
}

.press-thumb{
  display: flex;
  align-content: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.press-slider-thumbs .item img {  
  filter: grayscale(100%);
  opacity: .3;
  width: auto;
  max-height: 55px;
}

.press-slider-thumbs .active.current img{
  filter: grayscale(0);
  opacity: 1;
  
}

@media screen and (max-width: 767px){
  .press-slider-thumbs.owl-carousel{ display: none; }
}

.owl-theme .owl-nav [class*='owl-'] { 
  -webkit-transition: all .3s ease; transition: all .3s ease; 
}

.owl-theme .owl-nav [class*='owl-'].disabled:hover { 
  background-color: #D6D6D6; 
}

.press-slider.owl-theme { 
  position: relative; 
  padding: 2em 50px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
 
.press-slider .owl-stage{
  display: flex;
}

.press-slider p{
  font-size: clamp(15px, 2.9vw, 24px);
  max-width: 44em;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  margin-bottom: 0;
}
 
.press-slider.owl-carousel {
  position: relative;
}

.press-slider.owl-carousel .owl-nav span{
  color: #000;
}

.press-slider.owl-carousel .owl-nav button.owl-prev,
.press-slider.owl-carousel .owl-nav button.owl-next{
  left: 0;
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  font-size: 2.5em;
  width: 1.25em;
  height: 1.25em; 
  margin-top: -.5em;
}

.owl-theme .owl-nav [class*="owl-"]:hover{
  background: none;
}

.press-slider.owl-carousel  .owl-nav  button.owl-next{
  right: 0;
  left: auto;
  
}

.press-slider.owl-carousel button.owl-prev span, 
.press-slider.owl-carousel button.owl-next span{
  color: #222;
  font-size: 1em;
}

.press-slider.owl-carousel button.owl-prev:active span, 
.press-slider.owl-carousel button.owl-next:active span{
  top: calc(50% + 2px);
}
 
.testimonial-logo{
  width: 150px;
  margin: auto auto 0;
  flex-grow: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

@media screen and (min-width: 768px){
  .testimonial-logo{ display: none; }
}

</style></div><div class="text-block poppins" data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-element="main"><h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>People Are&nbsp;Talking&hellip;</strong></h2></div><div data-content-type="html" data-appearance="default" data-element="main" data-decoded="true"><!-- Press Carousel | HTML -->
<div class="press-slider-container">
  <div id="big" class="press-slider owl-carousel owl-theme">
    <div class="item"> 
      <h3>PopSugar</h3>
      <p>"Maren's bronzed makeup look was inspired by her rose-gold LBV dress…. JOAH Beauty products helped us create a simple yet sophisticated look."</p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/popsugar.png" alt="PopSugar" loading="lazy"/></div>  
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>WWD</h3>
      <p>"JOAH Brow Down To Me Precision Brow Pencil even comes with a spoolie brush at its impressively low price. It has an ultra-fine tip, allowing you to draw on hair-like strokes that look like the real deal. The creamy formula has serious staying power."</p>
       
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/wwd.png" alt="WWD" loading="lazy"/></div> 
    </div>

    <div class="item"> 
      <h3>Style Bistro</h3>
      <p>"JOAH Beauty is a cruelty-free brand that embraces the Korean beauty philosophy that beauty begins with the skin. From their mascaras to their eyeliners and lipsticks, this trendy brand offers an array of must-have items."</p>
       
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/stylebistro.png" alt="Style Bistro" loading="lazy"/></div> 
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Self</h3>
      <p>"For an easy, budget-friendly alternative, I typically recommend the Joah Brow Down to Me Precision Pencil. It has a fine tip, which creates strokes that mimic hair."</p>
     
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/self.png" alt="Self" loading="lazy"/></div> 
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Glamour</h3> 
      <p>"I would take Joah’s Tinted Moisturizer stick, which is luminous and creates a great, even base,” she says, adding that using a buffing brush will help you get an even finish. </p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/glamour.png" alt="Glamour" loading="lazy"/></div> 
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>HelloGiggles</h3>
      <p>This mascara coats and conditions each lash to amplify volume, lift, and lengthen—and it’s formulated to keep the product lightweight and airy (no droopy lashes here!). </p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/hello-giggles.png" alt="HelloGiggles" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>  
  
    <div class="item">
      <h3>Allure</h3>
      <p>Joah Lash Uprising Mascara is a fantastic place to start. It's a do-it-all formula that promises well-defined, longer, thicker lashes, all while being undetectably lightweight.</p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/allure.png" alt="Allure" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Allure</h3>
      <p>Joah Beauty's Crystal Glow Tinted Luminizer Stick… K-beauty-inspired product might look like a standard stick foundation, but it sets itself far apart from the pack with very sheer coverage and a shimmery sheen that gives an instant glass-skin effect.</p>
     
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/allure.png" alt="Allure" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>  

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Byrdie</h3>
      <p>Say goodbye to smudging, this is the best lip-liner you could wear for a swim. Silky and non-sliding, this intense formula glides around your lips effortlessly.</p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/byrdie.png" alt="Byrdie" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>  

    <div class="item">
      <h3>OK</h3>
       
      <p>Joah Beauty Crystal Glow Tinted Luminizer Stick- So luminous! Use on any area of the face in need of an extra dewy finish.</p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/ok.png" alt="OK Magazine" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Rouge 18</h3>
      <p>Crystal Glow Tinted Luminizer Stick is a multitasking stick for highlighting, contouring, or all over glow that can be worn alone or under makeup.</p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/rogue18.png" alt="Rouge 18" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>BuzzFeed</h3>
      <p>A tinted luminizer stick you can wear like foundation, use as a highlighter, or mask undereye circles. It's super creamy and stays put! Plus that brush on the other end makes it even easier to blend in.</p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/buzzfeed.png" alt="BuzzFeed" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Bella</h3>
      <p><strong>GOLD RUSH</strong></p>
      <p>JOAH Glow Activator Radiance Primer is a lightweight, universal primer that will always have you ready to glow. Infused with real, luminous 24k gold flakes to achieve a dewy, subtle glow, this product will leave your skin feeling hydrated and smooth with renewed radiance. </p>
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/bella.png" alt="Bella" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>SPA &amp; Beauty</h3>
       
      <p>JOAH Beauty’s Crystal Glow Collection officially launched today and the product line provides everything you need to achieve a dewy glow, even if you’re just glowing from home. </p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/spa-beauty.png" alt="SPA &amp; Beauty" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>  

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Allure</h3>
      <p>The Tinted Luminizer Stick from the line, is the ultimate complexion multi-tasker. With a lightweight and dewy finish, it can be used as a subtle skin tint, layered up as a foundation, or as a wet-looking highlighter when applied to the high points of the face.</p>
      
      <div class="testimonial-logo"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20230407022305im_/https://www.joahbeauty.com/media/wysiwyg/joah/home-page2-0/press-slider/allure.png" alt="Allure" loading="lazy"/></div>
    </div>  
</div>

